gvcfgenotyper
------------------------------------------
Utility for merging and genotyping Illumina-style GVCFs

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libfmt12-12.1.0-1bl1
  libgcc1-14.4.0-1
  libhts3-1.23.1-1bl1
  libspdlog1.17-1.17.0-1bl1
  libstdc++6-14.4.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-14.4.0-1
  libfmt-devel-12.1.0-1bl1
  libhts-devel-1.23.1-1bl1
  libspdlog-devel-1.17.0-1bl1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/Illumina/gvcfgenotyper

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/Illumina/gvcfgenotyper/archive/refs/tags/2019.02.26.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack gvcfgenotyper-2019.02.26-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./gvcfgenotyper-2019.02.26-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/gvcfgenotyper-2019.02.26-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/gvcfgenotyper-2019.02.26-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(gvcfgenotyper)
  /usr/bin/gvcfgenotyper.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/gvcfgenotyper.README
  /usr/share/doc/gvcfgenotyper/LICENSE.txt
  /usr/share/doc/gvcfgenotyper/README.md

